133
00:07:04,844 --> 00:07:06,125
I wonder how Captain Jin
deals with that?

134
00:07:06,245 --> 00:07:06,925
Captain Jin is there.

135
00:07:07,844 --> 00:07:08,524
Captain Jin.

136
00:07:10,605 --> 00:07:11,204
- Captain Jin.
- Captain Jin.

137
00:07:12,404 --> 00:07:13,125
