433
00:23:11,765 --> 00:23:12,605
I've regretted it.

434
00:23:12,924 --> 00:23:13,724
Just words.

435
00:23:13,885 --> 00:23:14,684
You have no proof.

436
00:23:17,565 --> 00:23:19,204
I said we were over.

437
00:23:19,684 --> 00:23:20,525
I don't have the mood

438
00:23:20,565 --> 00:23:21,164
